---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Areas Served | San Diego Commercial Cleaning | B & G Southwest"
  description="B & G Southwest provides premium commercial surface care across San Diego County, including Sorrento Valley, Carlsbad, Downtown, and Kearny Mesa."
>
  <header class="hero" style="min-height: 50vh;">
    <img src="/img/hero-areas.png" alt="Aerial view of downtown San Diego" class="hero-bg" fetchpriority="high">
    <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; padding-top: 4rem;">
        <h1 style="color: white;">Serving <span>San Diego County</span></h1>
        <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #cbd5e1;">Rapid, reliable deployment of commercial surface care teams across the greater San Diego region.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section-padding container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <h2>Our Local Footprint</h2>
          <p>Because our operations are built on an efficient dispatch methodology, our teams are highly mobile and efficiently routed throughout San Diego County. We service millions of square feet nightly across these key business districts:</p>

          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>Sorrento Valley</strong> (Tech & Biotech)</li>
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>Carlsbad</strong> (Corporate HQs)</li>
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>Downtown San Diego</strong> (High-Rises)</li>
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>Kearny Mesa</strong> (Industrial & Retail)</li>
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>La Jolla / UTC</strong> (Medical & Executive)</li>
            <li style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-amber);"><strong>Mission Valley</strong> (Retail & Office)</li>
          </ul>

          <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h3>Don't see your specific city?</h3>
            <p>If you manage a commercial facility within San Diego County borders, our logistics teams can likely accommodate your site. <a href="/contact">Contact dispatch</a> for route availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background: var(--bg-primary-dark); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 3rem; color: white;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--brand-amber); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Why Local Routing Matters</h3>
          <p style="color: #cbd5e1;">In the event of an unexpected facility spill, flood, or audit, response time is critical. Our centralized dispatch in San Diego ensures that a specialized extraction or restoration unit can be redeployed to your site without the logistical drag of out-of-county travel.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem; width: 100%;">Schedule a Local Walkthrough</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
